! GNV Bash 1.14.8 does a special expand_words_for_internal_comand()
! before execute_subshell_builtin_or_function()
! As near as I can tell, this code is not normally used, and there
! are other ways to do what it was inserted for with out changing bash.

!
! GNV Bash 1.14.8 had in incomplete and incorrect sequence of code
! here for restoring parent context and executing parent code. It
! has been replaced with what you see below.
!------------------------------------------------------------------
